research/history/logs/agent_action_0037.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","reference_round":27,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"lowrank_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","needs_sanity":true,"hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈T(x)} γ_j(x) c_j。这里 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线侧先计算 trunk 系数 β_r(x)，再用轻量 router 选择单个 expert 子库 e(x) 并在其内做局部 sparse 选择，最后对剩余残差再做一次小预算 sparse 补偿。因此它仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“查表 + 加权求和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判定为扩展兼容。主假设是：在与 r27 相同的 EF=1、K=192 recipe 下，把 `expert_topk` 升级为 `lowrank + expert + residual` 三段式结构，能回答‘仅有 lowrank+expert 仍不足时，加入第二段 residual 修正是否会形成新的结构性 Pareto 段’这个当前更关键的问题。","summary":"不继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上做第三个邻域扫点，而是进入下一结构槽位：实现最小可运行的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 原型。以 r27 的 `expert_topk K=192 EF=1` 为 matched baseline，只改 `ARCHITECTURE`，先验证三段式结构本身是否值得继续。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：运行配置相对 r27 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮优先解决结构未知量，而不是继续在已显示弱势的 recipe 上局部打磨。选择 r27 而不是 r34/r18，是因为它提供了与 expert 路由最接近的 matched baseline，同时避免把结论混入 jumprelu 或大 K 主线。风险是该三段式原型在 K=192 处总成本大概率落在中成本带而非极低成本带，但这仍符合当前阶段允许用少量中成本质量锚点回答结构问题的策略。","next_hypotheses":["如果 `lowrank_expert_residual` 首轮能稳定训练且 FVU 明显优于 `expert_topk K=192`，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 expert 段与 residual 段的预算分配是否是主要控制旋钮。","如果该 family 训练稳定但收益有限，下一轮优先只改 `TRUNK_RANK`，验证 trunk 是否过重并侵蚀了低成本收益。","如果三段式 family 连 matched baseline 都无法明显改善，应停止继续围绕该原型打磨，转向 `two-stage residual expert` 方向，而不是回到 plain selector 家族。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的导出形式是 trunk 静态库 + 单 expert 静态子库 + residual 静态补偿库上的有限加权和，属于扩展兼容 family，不是动态字典。","本轮要回答的是三段式 `lowrank + expert + residual` 是否值得继续，而不是再问一次 `expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴斜率。","建议实现时复用现有 lowrank trunk、expert local top-k、以及 residual second-pass 模块，避免新增 tunable 名称；优先复用现有 `TRUNK_RANK` 与 `STAGE1_RATIO` 语义。","若新增 family 需要后续调 `TRUNK_RANK`/`STAGE1_RATIO`，应同时补齐该 architecture 在 override registry 中的允许键，避免后续 param_only 回合静默拒绝 override。"],"touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0090.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E(z(x))} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(z(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d z(x)=Bx \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u7ef4\u6295\u5f71\uff0cE(z) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0cexpert \u5185\u7528\u5c0f\u578b low-rank head A_e z \u505a local scoring/top-k\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u201cshared low-rank projection + \u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u9009\u62e9 + \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\u7684 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r86 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `K=128`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=16`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u5982\u679c r86 \u7684\u5931\u8d25\u4e3b\u8981\u6765\u81ea full-dim routed scorer \u592a\u91cd\u800c\u4e0d\u662f multi-expert MoE-like \u672c\u8eab\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 shared-basis expert routing \u5e94\u80fd\u5728\u66f4\u4f4e total_cost \u4e0b\u663e\u8457\u6539\u5584 FVU\uff0c\u5e76\u5728 0.3x \u5de6\u53f3\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u5f62\u6210\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u6027 anchor\u3002\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u6210\u672c\u6a21\u578b\u7c97\u4f30\uff0cselection\u22480.19x\u3001deployment\u22480.12x\u3001total\u22480.31x\uff0c\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002",
