research/history/logs/agent_action_0066.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库；在线可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r65 仅把 TRUNK_RANK 从 32 降到 24，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EF=1` 不变时，继续压缩 encoder 与部署侧的 trunk 成本；如果 r65 的收益主要来自“三段式结构本身”而非 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 这个具体宽度，则该点应以更低 total_cost 保住大部分质量，并在 <0.5x 带形成更靠左的新 Pareto 点。","summary":"r65 已经证明把 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的 trunk 从 64 压到 32 仍能保住可用质量，并把 total_cost 拉回 0.49x。Round 66 不改 family、不改 K，只继续小步压 `TRUNK_RANK`，直接回答这条三段式结构还能否在低成本带进一步左移。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r65 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。该 family 属于 LUTurbo 扩展兼容 family，不触碰不兼容方向，也不需要新增 tunable 参数接线。选择 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 而不是再次压 `K` 或切 family，是因为 r65 已经给出正信号，而最近对 `K`、`STAGE1_RATIO` 和 `two_stage_residual_expert` 的尝试都没有带来更优结构性信息；当前最清晰的问题是 r65 这条新低成本三段式前沿还能否继续左移。主要风险是 trunk 再压缩后 FVU 回退过多；但即便如此，也能较清晰地界定这条 family 在当前 target 上的最小可用 trunk 宽度。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"24"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 目前已在 `TRUNK_RANK=32, K=128, NUM_EXPERTS=32` 下拿到新的 0.49x 低成本锚点；下一步优先判断它能否继续左移，而不是再做 family 切换。","Round 66 是对 r65 的纯 encoder-cost compression probe：只降 `TRUNK_RANK`，保持其他结构预算不变。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 仍保住接近 r65 的 FVU，则说明这条三段式结构在当前 target 上仍有低成本压缩空间。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 仍接近 r65，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=16` 或 `TRUNK_RANK=28/32`，细化三段式低成本 Pareto 段。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 明显退化，则说明 r65 附近已接近这条 family 的低成本极限；后续低成本预算应回投 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或新的 MoE-like 方向。","如果结果异常，先核对 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `trunk_rank=24` 是否真实生效，再决定是否把该轮当作结构证据。"],"reference_round":65}
research/history/logs/agent_action_0102.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_expert_topk"},{"key":"EXPANSION_FACTOR","value":"1"},{"key":"K","value":"128"},{"key":"HOOKPOINTS","value":"layers.[3].self_attn.q_proj"},{"key":"OPTIMIZER","value":"adam"},{"key":"LR","value":"8e-4"},{"key":"BATCH_SIZE","value":"1"},{"key":"GRAD_ACC_STEPS","value":"8"},{"key":"MICRO_ACC_STEPS","value":"1"},{"key":"AUXK_ALPHA","value":"0.03125"},{"key":"DEAD_FEATURE_THRESHOLD","value":"10000000"},{"key":"USE_HADAMARD","value":"0"},{"key":"COMPILE_MODEL","value":"1"},{"key":"NUM_EXPERTS","value":"32"},{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设不变：shared+routed 异构子库能在保持 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 短激活路径的同时补足 routed-only MoE 的通用容量，并在约 total_cost=0.63x 的中低成本带形成比 routed-only `expert_topk` 更强的结构性 anchor；本轮先修复上轮把 `NUM_EXPERTS/ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 错判为非法 override 的执行层 blocker，让该假设得到真实训练验证。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该修复后首轮真实训练完成且信号积极，下一步优先给 shared+routed 结构叠加 low-rank trunk，验证是否能把同类结构推回 <0.5x total_cost。","如果该修复后训练可跑但 FVU 仍明显弱于 `lowrank_expert_topk`，则说明 shared 容量本身不足以替代 trunk，应把后续预算转向 `lowrank + shared+routed expert` 而不是继续做 trunk-free 细扫。","如果仍出现 crash，应继续按新失败栈修实现或参数接线，不把结果误判成 shared+routed 结构负结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["Round 101 的真实 blocker 已定位为 override allowlist 缺项，而不是 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 前向/反向实现问题。","已在 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py` 把 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 接入 `_EXPERT_KEYS`；本地 `validate_env_overrides(...)` 对 `NUM_EXPERTS=32, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 返回空列表。","本轮应复跑与 r101 相同的 shared+routed prototype 配方，先确认 round config 与 checkpoint config 中 `num_experts=32`、`active_experts=1` 真实落地。"],"reference_round":null,"self_review":"这轮是工程修复，不重新设计实验，也不改结构假设。改动限制在允许范围内的 `research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`，目标是解除最近一轮的执行层 blocker，让原始 shared+routed 原型得到有效训练证据。","summary":"修复 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 override allowlist 后，重跑上轮被执行层拦截的同一 prototype 配方，先拿到真实训练信号。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py"]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0078.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_e \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d e(x) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5355\u4e2a expert\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201crouter \u9009\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93 + \u5b50\u5e93\u5185 local top-k + \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5148\u7b5b\u6e05\u695a\uff1a`expert_topk` \u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`factorized_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`two_stage_residual_expert` \u5c5e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002r77 \u5df2\u7ecf\u7ed9\u51fa\u6e05\u6670\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a`factorized_expert_topk` \u5728\u4e0e r74 \u8fd1\u540c\u6210\u672c\u7684 matched probe \u4e0b FVU=0.2482\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d `expert-internal low-rank / shared-basis` \u539f\u578b\u4e0d\u503c\u5f97\u7ee7\u7eed\u4f5c\u4e3a\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u4e3b\u7ebf\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r74 \u4ec5\u628a `K` \u4ece 160 \u63d0\u5230 192\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=128`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54 routed-only MoE-like \u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u524d\u6cbf\u7684\u4e0b\u4e00\u5173\u952e\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5982\u679c r73\u2192r74 \u7684\u8fde\u7eed\u6539\u5584\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u7684\u4e3b\u74f6\u9888\u4ecd\u6709\u4e00\u90e8\u5206\u6765\u81ea\u6bcf token \u7684\u5c40\u90e8 lookup budget \u4e0d\u8db3\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u53ea\u662f\u603b\u5bb9\u91cf\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48\u5728\u4fdd\u6301\u540c\u4e00\u5bb9\u91cf\u4e0e\u77ed active path \u7684\u524d\u63d0\u4e0b\uff0c\u9002\u5ea6\u589e\u52a0 `K` \u5e94\u80fd\u5728\u4ecd\u4f4e\u4e8e 0.5x total_cost \u7684\u8303\u56f4\u5185\u7ee7\u7eed\u538b\u4f4e FVU\uff0c\u5e76\u5224\u65ad routed-only \u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u7ebf\u6b64\u523b\u66f4\u7f3a\u5bb9\u91cf\u8fd8\u662f\u66f4\u7f3a lookup budget\u3002",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0078.json:25:    "self_review": "\u6ee1\u8db3\u5355\u8f6e\u5355\u53d8\u91cf\u7ea6\u675f\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r74 \u53ea\u6539 `K`\u3002\u8fd9\u4e0d\u662f plain selector \u7684\u65e7\u5f0f K \u8f74\u7ec6\u626b\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u53c2\u8003\u70b9\u672c\u8eab\u662f\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7 MoE-like sparse-capacity recipe `NUM_EXPERTS=128`\uff0c\u800c\u672c\u8f6e\u662f\u5728 r77 \u5df2\u660e\u786e\u5426\u5b9a shared-basis \u539f\u578b\u540e\uff0c\u5bf9 routed-only \u524d\u6cbf\u505a\u7684\u74f6\u9888\u5206\u89e3 probe\u3002\u4e3b\u8981\u98ce\u9669\u662f\u6539\u5584\u53ef\u80fd\u5f88\u5c0f\uff1b\u4f46\u5373\u4fbf\u5982\u6b64\u4e5f\u6709\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u82e5 `K=192` \u5728\u8be5 recipe \u4e0b\u4ecd\u65e0\u660e\u663e\u6536\u76ca\uff0c\u5c31\u53ef\u66f4\u6e05\u6670\u5224\u5b9a\u5f53\u524d `expert_topk` \u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u74f6\u9888\u5df2\u4e0d\u4e3b\u8981\u5728 lookup budget\uff0c\u540e\u7eed\u5e94\u628a\u7ed3\u6784\u9884\u7b97\u8f6c\u56de `lowrank_expert_residual` \u7684 trunk/stage \u8f74\u6216\u5176\u4ed6\u517c\u5bb9 family\u3002",
