research/history/logs/agent_round_0068.stdout.log:328:    "按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 估算，`lowrank_expert_topk K=128 TRUNK_RANK=64 NUM_EXPERTS=64` 的成本约为 selection 0.30x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.48x。",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0068.stdout.log:329:    "本轮是对 r60 的 true sparse-capacity continuation：只增大总 expert 容量，不增加 active experts，也不改 K/TRUNK_RANK。"
research/history/logs/agent_round_0068.stdout.log:332:    "如果 NUM_EXPERTS=64 在近同成本下显著优于 r60，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 NUM_EXPERTS=128，确认低成本段的容量收益是否继续成立。",
