research/history/logs/agent_round_0097.stdout.log:380:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":95,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_cost","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"112"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r95 (`K=128`) 与 r96 (`K=96`) 已经把当前有效主线 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 deployment-knee 两端都测出来，但中间缺少 `K=112` 这个最关键的边界点。相对 r95 仅将 `K: 128 -> 112`，在保持 `TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变时，如果当前质量退化主要发生在 `K<112` 之后，那么 `K=112` 应能明显优于 r96 的 0.1305，同时把 total_cost 从 r95 的同配方进一步左移到约 0.43x（按当前 fresh cost 粗估），从而完成 `K=96-128` 边界定位。","summary":"当前不要继续细扫 `TRUNK_RANK`，也不要回到 routed-only 或 `factorized_expert_topk` 这些已给出负信号的方向。以 r95 为 reference，只改 `K=112`，把 `lowrank_expert_topk` 当前主线 recipe 的 `K=96-128` 压缩边界补完整；这是 operator guide 明确要求优先完成的 knee 定位步骤。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r95 只改 `K`。这不是 old-family 的普通 K 轴回退，因为当前 <0.5x 有效主线已经明确是 `lowrank_expert_topk`，且 r95/r96 正好留下一个高信息量的边界缺口。主要风险是 `K=112` 结果只是落在 r95 和 r96 的平滑插值线上而不形成新的非支配点；但即便如此，也能完成当前阶段明确要求的 `K=96-128` knee 定位，避免继续在未封口的边界上盲目切 family。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r95 (`lowrank_expert_topk TRUNK_RANK=40 K=128`) 与 r96 (`K=96`) 已证明当前低成本主线的 deployment budget 不是全-or-nothing，而是存在可继续压缩的空间。","当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 K 轴还缺少 `K=112` 这一中间点；补齐它比立即切去 `lowrank_expert_residual` 更符合 Round 97 的 runtime priority。","`factorized_expert_topk` 与 routed-only `ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 方向都已给出稳定负信号，本轮继续留在当前有效主线上更合理。","按当前 fresh cost 粗估，`lowrank_expert_topk K=112 NUM_EXPERTS=32 TRUNK_RANK=40` 的 selection 基本不变，deployment 低于 `K=128`，total_cost 约 0.43x，仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=112` 形成新的非支配中间点，则 `K=96-128` 边界已基本完成，下一轮应切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual` 结构对照，而不是继续在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上细扫。","如果 `K=112` 基本贴着 r95-r96 的平滑插值且不形成新前沿，则说明当前 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 deployment-knee 已足够清楚；下一轮同样应切到 matched `lowrank_expert_residual`。","如果 `K=112` 意外明显劣化并接近 r96，则可判定当前主线对 deployment budget 比预期更敏感；下一轮应回到 `K=128` 配方，并优先测试 matched residual cleanup 是否值得其额外成本。"]}
research/history/round_summaries/round_0075.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_e \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d e(x) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5355\u4e2a expert\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201crouter \u9009\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93 + \u5b50\u5e93\u5185 local top-k + \u67e5\u8868\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5148\u7b5b\u6e05\u695a\uff1a`expert_topk` \u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r74 \u4ec5\u628a `NUM_EXPERTS` \u4ece 128 \u63d0\u5230 256\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk`\u3001`K=160`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u56de\u7b54 routed-only MoE-like \u524d\u6cbf\u7684\u6838\u5fc3\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u5982\u679c r73\u2192r74 \u7684\u8fde\u7eed\u6539\u5584\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u7684\u4e3b\u8981\u74f6\u9888\u4ecd\u6709\u4e00\u90e8\u5206\u6765\u81ea\u603b\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u5bb9\u91cf\u4e0d\u8db3\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f router \u8d28\u91cf\u6216 K \u9884\u7b97\u5df2\u7ecf\u9971\u548c\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u6269\u5927\u603b\u5bb9\u91cf\u3001\u540c\u65f6\u4fdd\u6301 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` \u7684\u77ed\u6fc0\u6d3b\u8def\u5f84\uff0c\u5e94\u80fd\u5728\u4ecd\u5904\u4e8e <0.5x \u7684\u8fd1\u540c\u4e00 total_cost \u4e0b