research/history/logs/agent_action_0083.json:3:  "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + residual 查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r79 与 r81 已表明继续动 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或继续压 `TRUNK_RANK` 会退化，r82 又表明在 `lowrank_expert_topk` 上把 expert 粒度压粗到 16 会明显变差；因此当前最值得回答的问题是：在保留 residual cleanup 的三段式主线里，更粗的 expert 粒度是否仍然可行。相对 r76 只把 `NUM_EXPERTS` 从 64 降到 16，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`TRUNK_RANK=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余训练配方不变时，直接测试 residual 分支是否足以弥补更粗 expert 划分带来的局部容量损失，并在几乎不增部署成本的前提下把 selection cost 再向左推一小段。如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的粗 expert 失败主要因为缺少 residual cleanup，那么这个三段式 family 仍有机会在低到中成本带形成新的 Pareto 段。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0083.json:4:  "summary": "Round 83 不回到 plain selector 的 K/LR 微调，也不重复已经给出负信号的 `TRUNK_RANK` / `STAGE1_RATIO` 轴，而是回到当前最强的兼容三段式主线 `lowrank_expert_residual` 做一次高信息量 expert 粒度 probe。以 r76 为 reference，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=16`，验证 residual cleanup 是否能让更粗的 expert 子库在低到中成本带保持质量，从而补出新的结构性前沿。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0083.json:10:  "self_review": "满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r76 只改 `NUM_EXPERTS`。这比继续扫 `K`、继续压 `TRUNK_RANK`、继续调 `STAGE1_RATIO`，或回到已被 r82 进一步否定的 `lowrank_expert_topk` expert 粒度轴更符合当前证据，因为最近四轮已经分别否定了 higher stage1 budget、trunk compression、trunk-free staged、以及无 residual 的粗 expert 路线。当前最有信息量的问题是：`lowrank + expert + residual` 是否能依靠 residual cleanup 支撑更粗的 expert 划分，从而把这条 family 的低成本段进一步左移。主要风险是 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 同样会因为局部专门化不足而退化；但无论正负，都能直接回答 residual 分支到底有没有把 MoE-like 粒度空间重新打开。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0083.json:14:      "key": "NUM_EXPERTS",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0083.json:21:    "按当前成本模型估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=32 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 NUM_EXPERTS=16` 仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，combined ratio 约 0.68，略低于 r76 的约 0.69。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0083.json:22:    "r82 说明没有 residual cleanup 的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 下明显退化；Round 83 用 matched 三段式 recipe 复测同一粒度方向，专门判断 residual 分支是否改变 coarse-expert 结论。"
research/history/logs/agent_action_0083.json:25:    "如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 接近或优于 r76，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=160`，确认更粗 expert 粒度下这条三段式主线是否能沿 deployment 侧继续改善。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0083.json:26:    "如果 `NUM_EXPERTS=16` 明显退化，则可较清楚地判断当前 target 上 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的有效 expert 粒度已经不宜再压粗，后续应把预算转向更高信息量的新结构方向，而不是继续在现有粒度轴上细扫。",
research/history/logs/agent_action_0083.json:27:    "如果结果接近但不明确，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=32` 或 `48` 做更窄的 matched 对照，确认这条三段式主线的最佳 expert 粒度区间。"
research/history/round_summaries/round_0081.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{r=1..R} \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(x)}(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + \u03a3_j \u03b3_j(x) c_j\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d U={u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0cC={c_j} \u662f\u9759\u6001 residual \u8865\u507f\u5e93\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868 + \u5355 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + residual \u8865\u507f\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_residual` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5148\u7b5b\u6e05\u695a\uff1a`expert_topk` \u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`lowrank_expert_topk`\u3001`lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`two_stage_residual_expert`\u3001`factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002r79 \u4e0e r80 \u5df2\u8fde\u7eed\u7ed9\u51fa\u6e05\u6670\u8d1f\u4fe1\u53f7\uff1a\u628a `STAGE1_RATIO` \u4ece 0.25 \u63d0\u5230 0.5 \u4f1a\u53d8\u5dee\uff0c\u800c\u53bb\u6389 low-rank trunk \u7684 `two_stage_residual_expert` \u4e5f\u660e\u663e\u5f31\u4e8e matched `lowrank_expert_residual`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u5f53\u524d\u4f4e\u5230\u4e2d\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u91cc trunk \u4ecd\u662f\u5fc5\u8981\u7ec4\u6210\uff0c\u4e14\u66f4\u5f3a residual cleanup \u6bd4\u66f4\u9ad8 expert-stage \u9884\u7b97\u66f4\u91cd\u8981\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r76 \u4ec5\u628a `TRUNK_RANK` \u4ece 32 \u964d\u5230 24\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`\u3001`K=128`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5173\u952e\u7684\u4f4e\u6210\u672c\u95ee\u9898\uff1a\u65e2\u7136 routed-only\u3001shared-basis\u3001stage split\u3001\u4ee5\u53ca trunk-free staged \u8def\u7ebf\u90fd\u672a\u5e26\u6765\u66f4\u4f18\u7ed3\u6784\u6bb5\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 `lowrank + expert + residual` \u8fd9\u6761\u5f53\u524d\u6700\u5f3a\u517c\u5bb9\u4e3b\u7ebf\u8fd8\u80fd\u5426\u4ec5\u901a\u8fc7\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u538b\u7f29\u5fc5\u8981 trunk \u5bbd\u5ea6\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301\u5927\u90e8\u5206\u8d28\u91cf\u7684\u540c\u65f6\u628a total_cost \u518d\u5f80\u5de6\u63a8\u4e00\u5c0f\u6bb5\uff0c\u5e76\u5f62\u6210\u6bd4 r76 \u66f4\u7ecf\u6d4e\u7684\u65b0 Pareto \u70b9\u3002",
