research/history/logs/agent_round_0068.stdout.log:452:{"round": 67, "hypothesis": "最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选出的单个 expert。在线侧仍可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”流水线，不依赖动态生成字典，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r60 仅把 NUM_EXPERTS 从 32 提到 64，在保持 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk、K=128、TRUNK_RANK=64、EF=1、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 不变时，如果当前 0.48x 左右低成本段的瓶颈仍有一部分来自 routed static capacity 不足，而不只是 shared trunk 太薄，那么更大的总 expert 子库容量应在几乎同一 total_cost 下继续压低 FVU，并回答 true sparse-capacity MoE-like 扩容在当前 target 上是否还能形成新的低成本 Pareto 段。", "change_type": "param_only", "expected_win": "explore_unknown", "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk", "family_stage": "prototype", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.11357318609952927", "observed_fvu": "0.113573", "k": "128", "architecture": "lowrank_expert_topk", "touched_files": [], "run_health": "perf_regression", "termination_reason": "throughput_too_low", "tokens_per_sec": "34971.062849", "baseline_ratio": "0.209974"}
