research/history/logs/agent_round_0085.stdout.log:38254:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"2"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x-t(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，|E(x-t(x))|=ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2。在线导出仍是“trunk 查表 + 2 个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。相对 r60 仅新增 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2，在保持 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk、K=128、TRUNK_RANK=64、NUM_EXPERTS=32、EXPANSION_FACTOR=1、OPTIMIZER=adam、LR=8e-4 不变时，验证 shared trunk + routed experts 是否能通过更短于全容量扩张的 active path 提供新的 0.3x-0.8x total_cost Pareto 段。按当前成本模型估算，该点约为 encoder 0.54x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.73x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 在约 0.73x total_cost 下显著优于 r60，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 NUM_EXPERTS=64，验证“更大总容量 + 短 active path”是否继续成立。","如果 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 改善很弱或退化，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3 或回到 1，明确当前 target 的最优 active-expert 数，而不是继续混扫旧轴。","如果 lowrank_expert_topk 的多 expert active path 仍不给正信号，则后续把已接通的 ACTIVE_EXPERTS 转去 lowrank_expert_residual，测试 residual cleanup 是否比纯 routed topk 更需要多 expert。"],"notes_to_memory":["ACTIVE_EXPERTS 已完成最小必要接线：sparsify 配置/前向消费、override_registry、config_resolution、runner/runtime 持久化、audit/rebuild、scripts/autoresearch_test.sh 透传均已补齐。","expert_topk、factorized_expert_topk、lowrank_expert_topk、lowrank_expert_residual、two_stage_residual_expert 已本地 smoke 通过 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 的 forward/backward。","参数生效已验证：本地 validation run 的 checkpoint config.json 与 layer cfg.json 中都出现 active_experts=2；模拟的 round config 也解析出 active_experts=2。","当前 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 的 lowrank_expert_topk 成本估算约 total 0.73x，属于允许的中低成本结构性 anchor，而不是超预算点。"],"reference_round":60,"self_review":"这轮先修复了 r84 的真实 blocker，而不是把 override 拒绝误判成结构结论。相对 r60 的实际实验语义仍只新增一个 env 参数 ACTIVE_EXPERTS，因此归因保持单变量；代码改动也限制在允许范围内的 sparsify/、research/AutoResearch/、scripts/autoresearch_test.sh。主要风险是 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 会把 active expert scorer 成本从单 expert 提高到双 expert，total_cost 从约 0.48x 抬到约 0.73x；如果 FVU 改善不足，这条 MoE-like active-path 扩展线就应尽快收缩。","summary":"已修复 ACTIVE_EXPERTS 的端到端接线并完成本地验证，现在可以重跑原本被 r84 阻塞的最小 MoE-like probe。建议本轮以 r60 为 reference，只加 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2，直接回答 lowrank_expert_topk 的 multi-expert active path 是否值得继续。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/__main__.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/config_resolution.py","research/AutoResearch/runner.py","research/AutoResearch/rebuild_runtime_state.py","research/AutoResearch/controller.py","research/AutoResearch/policy.py","research/AutoResearch/prompt.py","research/AutoResearch/audit_history_execution.py","scripts/autoresearch_test.sh"]}
